@startuml
title UC-08 Request to Create Course & Instructor Approval (Sequence)
participant Applicant
participant WebApp
participant ApplicationService
participant DB
participant NotificationService
participant Admin

Applicant -> WebApp: open instructor application & submit
WebApp -> ApplicationService: createApplication(payload)
ApplicationService -> DB: INSERT instructor_application(status=PENDING)
DB --> ApplicationService: created
ApplicationService -> NotificationService: notifyAdmins(application)
NotificationService -> Admin: in-app/email
ApplicationService --> WebApp: ack
WebApp --> Applicant: show pending status
@enduml
